<title type="html"><![CDATA[7/24 (Sat) Skydiving/ The Bucket List    ( Host: Howard)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=526&amp;p=549#p549"><![CDATA[
Let's join the Zoom meeting this Thursday at 07:00 pm<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw#success">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw#success</a><!-- m --><br /><br />會議 ID:929 8726 6213<br />密碼:112233<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Presentation 1<br />8:00-8:10 pm Break<br />8:10-8:40: Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation 2<br /><br />At the presentation, the time limit is 1-2 minutes for each speaker.<br /><br />Session I<br />skydiving<br />1. Have you ever tried skydiving? If yes, please share your experience with your group. If not, would you want to try? Why/ Why not?<br /><br />2. <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://wisconsinskydivingcenter.com/blog/skydiving-health-restrictions/">https://wisconsinskydivingcenter.com/bl ... trictions/</a><!-- m --><br />Is your body healthy enough to jump?<br /><br />3. Former US President George Bush Sr tried skydiving to mark his 80th, 85th, and 90th birthday. If you had been his children, how would have you thought about the condition?<br /><br /><br /><br />----------------------<br />Session II<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1RIOFzhufm8">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1RIOFzhufm8</a><!-- m --><br />The Bucket List (1/4) Movie CLIP - Skydiving (2007) HD<br /><br />Questions for Discussion<br />1.Their bucket list is to go skydiving, drive a Shelby Mustang, fly over the North Pole, eat dinner at Chevre d'or in France, visit and praise the beauty and history of Taj Mahal, India, ride motorcycles on the Great Wall of China, attend a lion safari in Tanzania and ..................................<br />Which item(s) do you love most? What's your own bucket list? Why do you list these items? <br />2. What item is your first priority to accomplish and why?<br />3. Carter and Edward cooperate and help each other to accomplish the bucket list. Do you think in the practical situation the mission will be ( a. easy b. impossible c. complicated d. your answer)<br /><br />-----------<br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=13721">morris</a> — Sat Jul 17, 2021 9:17 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
